description.text:
Building instructions contained in awing_instructions.pdf  
The .svg files contain the patterns for this model. They are designed for 1/8&quot; material. The reference square in awing_4.svg should measure 1&quot; x 1&quot;  
The laser guns are 1/4&quot; dowels. The 1/8&quot; barrels drilled down the center are optional but recommended.
